{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1363585, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大物到头了", "timestamp": 1617123790, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363591, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "雷系不是学计算机，望周知", "timestamp": 1617123826, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363603, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 刻板印象偏计算机(?) dbq", "timestamp": 1617123932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363670, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 唉 刻板印象也是有道理的，道理在于近年雷系热门的“出路”集中于CV，以及吸引眼球的雷课堂事件吧。不过雷系的核心确实是控制。", "timestamp": 1617124718, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363699, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "控制不可能和物理没关系，因为绝大多数被控对象都是存在于物理世界里的。雷系的一部分专业课，比如智能传感，比如智能机器人，肯定是要用一些物理的。雷系的电类课程是大头，不过其实这些并不完全算物理。数电、模电、电路原理、电力电子其实属于电子学。当然电子学的基础是电磁学的原理。雷系有门课叫电机拖动，现在合并到电能变换里了。这门课讲电机的原理，这里面是需要很多物理的。电怎么生磁，磁怎么生电。", "timestamp": 1617125075, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363757, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "雷系学的物理方面的东西偏电路，但没有像电子系学的深", "timestamp": 1617125842, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么雷系这么多做cv的啊", "timestamp": 1617126000, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1363879, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为雷系向计算机方向发展，一方面CV能够很好的结合之前对代码的学习，另一方面对数理基础要求不是很高，入门比较简单", "timestamp": 1617128238, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1365005, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: nlp对数理基础要求很高吗", "timestamp": 1617161674, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1365290, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 267809, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 因为模式识别是雷系的专长领域", "timestamp": 1617164125, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 267809, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "学计算机(贵软叉雷？)的同学会的物理多么（多于大物的程度）？一直很好奇学物理是不是挺容易被取代的（", "timestamp": 1617123670, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617164128, "url": "", "vote": {}}}